{"data":[{"id":24,"documentId":"ggcumeaki9hzbu7moe0c2fq8","title":"Home","slug":"home","createdAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.673Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-10T12:45:39.790Z","publishedAt":"2026-02-10T12:45:39.829Z","seo_title":"Di'aaru - Luxury Lab-Grown Diamonds | Ethical & Sustainable Fine Jewelry","seo_description":"Discover Di'aaru's exquisite collection of lab-grown diamonds. Ethically crafted, environmentally sustainable, and brilliantly beautiful. Each piece tells a story of timeless elegance and modern responsibility.","email":"customer@yopmail.com","phone":"+61 434 343 443","sections":[{"__component":"shared.hero-section","id":24,"heading":"Timeless Brilliance","sub_heading":"LUXURY LAB-GROWN DIAMONDS","description":"<p>Ethically crafted, infinitely beautiful. Discover diamonds that reflect not just light, but your values.</p>","button_text":"Explore Our Collection","button_link":"#products","isShow":true,"background_image":{"id":36,"documentId":"erk3ybbhakgrvque46eswswr","name":"diamond-hero","alternativeText":"diamond-hero","caption":"diamond-hero","focalPoint":null,"width":640,"height":640,"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_diamond-hero","hash":"thumbnail_diamond_hero_df788417c8","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":156,"height":156,"size":4.11,"sizeInBytes":4112,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_diamond_hero_df788417c8.png"},"small":{"name":"small_diamond-hero","hash":"small_diamond_hero_df788417c8","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":500,"height":500,"size":24.32,"sizeInBytes":24323,"url":"/uploads/small_diamond_hero_df788417c8.png"}},"hash":"diamond_hero_df788417c8","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":35.6,"url":"/uploads/diamond_hero_df788417c8.png","previewUrl":null,"provider":"local","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.133Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.133Z","publishedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.133Z"},"logo":null},{"__component":"shared.about-section","id":24,"title":"Our Story of Excellence","description":"<p>At Di'aaru, we believe that true luxury isn't just about beauty—it's about responsibility, craftsmanship, and timeless value.</p><p>Founded on the principle that exceptional diamonds should be accessible without compromising ethics or the environment, we've pioneered the art of creating laboratory-grown diamonds that are chemically, physically, and optically identical to mined diamonds.</p><p>Every Di'aaru diamond begins as a tiny seed in our state-of-the-art facility, where cutting-edge technology and centuries-old gemological knowledge combine to create stones of extraordinary brilliance. Our master craftsmen then transform these pristine diamonds into heirloom pieces that will be treasured for generations.</p><p>We're not just selling jewelry—we're offering a new way to celebrate life's precious moments, with beauty that comes from innovation rather than extraction.</p>","isShow":true,"image":{"id":37,"documentId":"ri97yhiitcycesep7cwr0o0z","name":"diamond-round","alternativeText":"diamond-round","caption":"diamond-round","focalPoint":null,"width":640,"height":640,"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_diamond-round","hash":"thumbnail_diamond_round_367723d62f","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":156,"height":156,"size":6.8,"sizeInBytes":6804,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_diamond_round_367723d62f.png"},"small":{"name":"small_diamond-round","hash":"small_diamond_round_367723d62f","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":500,"height":500,"size":38.41,"sizeInBytes":38408,"url":"/uploads/small_diamond_round_367723d62f.png"}},"hash":"diamond_round_367723d62f","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":53.23,"url":"/uploads/diamond_round_367723d62f.png","previewUrl":null,"provider":"local","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.197Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.197Z","publishedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:52.197Z"}},{"__component":"shared.product-section","id":24,"section_title":"Signature Collection","isShow":true,"products":[{"id":196,"documentId":"vc8pmyzgx6mt02kmutgd4tkk","name":"Eternal Solitaire Ring","slug":null,"description":"<p>A timeless masterpiece featuring a stunning 1.5-carat round brilliant lab-grown diamond set in 18K white gold. This classic solitaire design showcases the diamond's exceptional brilliance with a delicate four-prong setting that maximizes light reflection.</p><p>Each diamond is ethically created in our state-of-the-art facility, ensuring conflict-free sourcing and environmental responsibility.</p>","price":5999,"diamond_type":"Lab Grown","carat":1.5,"shape":"Round Brilliant","featured":true,"isShow":true,"createdAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.598Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.598Z","publishedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.606Z"},{"id":198,"documentId":"ggpwoa0uco7a9t8jtqhjrxlg","name":"Princess Cut Halo Engagement Ring","slug":null,"description":"<p>Exquisite princess cut center stone (2.0ct) surrounded by a halo of smaller brilliant diamonds, creating a stunning celestial effect. Set in platinum for ultimate durability and elegance.</p><p>The halo design adds approximately 0.5 carats of accent diamonds, enhancing the overall brilliance and making the center stone appear larger.</p>","price":8499,"diamond_type":"Lab Grown","carat":2,"shape":"Princess","featured":true,"isShow":true,"createdAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.722Z","updatedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.722Z","publishedAt":"2026-02-10T10:08:51.727Z"}]},{"__component":"shared.why-choose-us","id":24,"title":"The Di'aaru Difference","isShow":true,"features":[{"id":139,"feature_title":"Unmatched Quality","feature_description":"Every diamond is certified by leading gemological institutes with grades of D-F color and VS1 or better clarity. We never compromise on quality."},{"id":140,"feature_title":"Ethically Created","feature_description":"100% conflict-free and environmentally sustainable. Our lab-grown diamonds have 1/10th the carbon footprint of mined diamonds."},{"id":141,"feature_title":"Master Craftsmanship","feature_description":"Handcrafted by artisans with decades of experience. Each piece is individually inspected to meet our exacting standards."},{"id":142,"feature_title":"Lifetime Warranty","feature_description":"Comprehensive coverage including complimentary cleaning, resizing, and inspection. Your investment is protected forever."},{"id":143,"feature_title":"Exceptional Value","feature_description":"Lab-grown diamonds cost 40-60% less than mined equivalents, allowing you to choose a larger, higher-quality stone within your budget."},{"id":144,"feature_title":"Personalized Service","feature_description":"Dedicated jewelry consultants guide you through every step, from selection to customization, ensuring your vision becomes reality."}]},{"__component":"shared.gallery-section","id":24,"title":"Craftsmanship Gallery","isShow":true,"images":[{"id":44,"documentId":"kthe4af32ilbsfa4d2mxif5i","name":"Feb 10, 2026, 04_13_55 PM.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"focalPoint":null,"width":1536,"height":1024,"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_Feb 10, 2026, 04_13_55 PM.png","hash":"thumbnail_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":234,"height":156,"size":53.84,"sizeInBytes":53843,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e.png"},"small":{"name":"small_Feb 10, 2026, 04_13_55 PM.png","hash":"small_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":500,"height":333,"size":218.78,"sizeInBytes":218776,"url":"/uploads/small_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e.png"},"medium":{"name":"medium_Feb 10, 2026, 04_13_55 PM.png","hash":"medium_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","path":null,"width":750,"height":500,"size":477.01,"sizeInBytes":477007,"url":"/uploads/medium_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e.png"},"large":{"name":"large_Feb 10, 2026, 04_13_55 PM.png","hash":"large_Feb_10_2026_04_13_55_PM_e98375fc3e","ext":".png","mime":"image/p